WEBVTT

00:03:57.750 --> 00:04:00.726
I still longed for adventure.

00:04:00.750 --> 00:04:02.018
And this time,

00:04:02.042 --> 00:04:05.434
I started dreaming
of a grand outdoor adventure.

00:04:05.458 --> 00:04:08.917
And what's more grand
than the Grand Canyon?

00:04:09.875 --> 00:04:14.268
Did you know that for every
five million people who visit the Rim

00:04:14.292 --> 00:04:17.542
only one percent go down
to the canyon's base?

00:04:18.417 --> 00:04:21.393
I wanted to be a part of that one percent.

00:04:21.417 --> 00:04:22.934
The only thing is --

00:04:22.958 --> 00:04:27.309
(Applause)

00:04:27.333 --> 00:04:31.726
The only thing is that the Grand Canyon
isn't exactly accessible.